  "script": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The Fake Town"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": []
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "music",
          "ref": "lib-harvest-season",
          "label": "▶ Harvest Season"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "It's finally there, right in front of you."
        },
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "amb",
          "ref": "ambience/forest.mp3",
          "label": "〜 forest"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " Townton. You've spent days travelling trying to find this small community. The breeze carries with it the smell of cooked meat, cheers from a lively crowd, "
        },
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "amb",
          "ref": "ambience/fap-crowd.ogg",
          "label": "〜 fap-crowd"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "and smoke from the campfires"
        },
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "amb",
          "ref": "ambience/campfire.wav",
          "label": "〜 campfire"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ". Today is a good day. You spend the afternoon exploring the merry town. Joy on every face in this bustling crowd. You spend some time"
        },
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "music",
          "ref": "lib-minstrel-dance",
          "label": "▶ Minstrel Dance"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " at the local tavern where drinks flow and the attendants are rowdy. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": []
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "music",
          "ref": "lib-ruined-town",
          "label": "▶ Ruined Town"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Today was a good day. Almost too good. "
        },
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "amb",
          "ref": "ambience/dungeon-cave.ogg",
          "label": "〜 dungeon-cave"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "You stare at the folks and an eerie feeling creeps over you. They never stop smiling. They never stop eating, drinking, dancing, laughing. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": []
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Today is a strange day. As dusk fades darkness bring with it the rain and thunder. "
        },
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "amb",
          "ref": "ambience/rain-storm.ogg",
          "label": "〜 rain-storm"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Strange noises can be heard from outside of the wooden walls. "
        },
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "amb",
          "ref": "ambience/wind-whoosh.ogg",
          "label": "〜 wind-whoosh"
        },
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "music",
          "ref": "lib-tension-pursuit",
          "label": "▶ Tension Pursuit"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The winds pick up and bring in the noxiously sweet scent of death and rot. "
        },
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "sfx",
          "ref": "lib-bleach-hollow-scream-effect",
          "label": "🔊 Bleach Hollow Scream Effect"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "playlist": {
    "enabled": false
  }
}